11 An Act relating to medical records; amending 76 O.S.
2021, Section 19, which relates to access to medical
12 records; modifying applicability of certain
provisions; eliminating certain duties of health care
13 providers; authorizing imposition of certain fees;
modifying certain fee limits; defining terms; making
14 certain acts unlawful; creating misdemeanor offense;
providing administrative and criminal penalties;
15 providing for civil relief; and providing an
effective date.
