14 Dollars ($15.00). If the x-ray, other photograph, or image is
15 provided on a CD/DVD or other electronic media, the fee shall be
16 Twenty Dollars ($20.00) not more than Twenty-five Dollars ($25.00)
17 per CD/DVD or other electronic media. The physician, hospital, or
18 other medical professionals and institutions, or their business
19 associates as the term is defined in Section 160.103 of Title 45 of
